<h2>gridtext: Improved Text Rendering Support for 'Grid' Graphics</h2>
<p>Provides support for rendering of formatted text using 'grid' graphics. Text can be
    formatted via a minimal subset of 'Markdown', 'HTML', and inline 'CSS' directives, and it can be
    rendered both with and without word wrap.</p>
